rows.label: qev030608_MSG0001
rows.name:
Marriage? Ha! Heptana and Enneana both have sense
to reject my fool brother.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030608_MSG0002
rows.name:
If Nemard desires mate, he should be proper Prone
warrior. He has far to go before that day![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030608_MSG1001
rows.name: I cannot believe Heptana will be my brother's mate.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030608_MSG1002
rows.name:
There are many other Prone men.
Many stronger than Nemard.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030608_MSG2001
rows.name:
Grandfather Auld has been ill lately.
But he was still able to attend wedding.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030608_MSG2002
rows.name:
We were captured by Ganglion. It was hard on him.
It is good to see him happy again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030608_MSG3001
rows.name:
Marriage is powerful thing. My fool brother seemed
worthy of respect today. I should consider becoming
mate as well.[ST:wait ]
